ygData.messageBody:
Ok then, give me a tell whenever you come online....i will be online at
about 6 pm est time its 3 pm est now.

Ill look for you, oh if you want a sheild i have an extra chitin shell
sheild for sale, along with some other various items like silver antique
rings (plus 2 to ac each) and cutthroat rings (but you prob got them
already) and a couple other things i cant think of right now. Anyhow, ill
look for you as soon as i come online, or you look for me...ill see you then
and i look forward to partying with you!

Rayne T'Kazz
